---
title: Chimichurri Tofu & Spinach Grain Bowls with Mixed Sweet Potato Jumble
description: A colorful mix of orange and purple sweet potatoes adds delicious earthy-sweet flavor to these seared tofu and mixed grain bowls. Packed with fresh spinach and brightened up with herbaceous, tangy chimichurri sauce and fresh lemon juice, this nourishing meal is an instant winner as a light lunch or dinner.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/67d9292818d6e477003fcb03-b075c964.jpeg
